translation.Name: Buak_Note_46
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_4: Why does this number haunt me, I don't understand.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_5: Have I just fixated on it because I began to notice the pattern?
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_6: Is this a sign? Are you trying to tell me I'm on the right track?
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_7: Or are you just haunting me? You can't convince me it's a coincidence.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_8: You know you didn't need that flower. The cliff incident was your fault.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_9: I warned you, my sister has been dead for 40 years. Leave me alone until I'm ready.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_10: If you want to send signs, tell them what happened. Save me the effort.
